      "para_id": "Q001739.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Inana , the lady elevated as far as the heavens , the queen of the gods , his lady , Nammahni-dug , child of Lu-girizal , the governor of Lagaš , fashioned this ( statute ) , and built her temple ."
